The paper deals with survival analysis using convolutional neural networks on medical images, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of neural networks for feature extraction and prediction also suggests that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) sub-categories.
